description: Recently sold: $160,000. Welcome to lake life at its best! A recent addition (with partial basement) contributes nicely to the cabin's year-round functionality while adding to the overall square footage with plenty of space for entertaining family and friends. You could be living the lake life the way it was meant to be lived!

description:
Recently sold: $400,000. Hassle-free full ownership of a 4 bedroom / 3 bathroom home in lakeside luxury. Enjoy the income earning potential without the headaches of a typical rental unit. Just nine miles north of McGregor, this property is located within the Big Sandy Lodge & Resort. It's a premier Minnesota resort community located in the heart of northern Minnesota's vacationland on Big Sandy Lake; truly an up north vacation experience. 

The Resort is located minutes away from MN National Golf Course, a northern Minnesota 27 hole Joel Goldstrand Masterpiece. Big Sandy Lake is a 10,000 acre Reservoir lake (created in 1859) located only 2 hours north of the Twin Cities, 1 hour from Duluth and 1 hour from Brainerd. Big Sandy is a premier lake in the McGregor Lakes area and is home to Floe Manufacturing, an industry leader in dock, lifts, trailers and now boats. With numerous bar/restaurants located on the lake, from Zorbaz and Big Sandy Lodge & Resort to more traditional saloon style establishments, there is something for everyone when it comes to dining. Spend the day fishing, wake-boarding and the evenings cruising nearly 50 miles of shoreline in addition to great trails for snowmobiling and ATV.
